{"tid":1114853,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"我呀媽疑有被害妄想症 求幫助","createTime":"2019-04-18T17:38:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T16:07:36.000Z","uid":226975,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1666705b249cd5f000d55abe5243e9d5fa429b3e","tid":1114853,"uid":226975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T17:38:23.000Z","msg":"各位好。我都估唔到要係連登出呢個post 但係真係好無助。希望各位巴絲比少少意見。<br />\n<br />\n我呀媽自從有一份工好似比人玩。之後就疑神疑鬼，覺得住附近個個人都有份玩佢。街又唔出。封晒屋企啲窗。<br />\n<br />\n最近仲惡化左。主動去同隔離屋嘈交。<br />\n<br />\n之前想話帶佢去睇醫生。佢就反晒面。話我唔信佢。  <br />\n<br />\n我可以點幫佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a2dce029d7e80a2d3f9731477a3871ee261186","tid":1114853,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T17:39:09.000Z","msg":"辭職"},{"pid":"c1105e8d24e5d39987dff74895fb680ca07744cb","tid":1114853,"uid":132488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T17:46:29.000Z","msg":"捉佢唔係帶佢去睇醫生"},{"pid":"8b54b414e73c1b478dd0dadbdcb1b8f4d1649cec","tid":1114853,"uid":225760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T18:11:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06565ccac708e8fdec0946ed49629bc1084b15c1","tid":1114853,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T18:19:01.000Z","msg":"有啲社工可以上門，你搵日試下扮帶自己朋友上去囉，傾下計慢慢開始"},{"pid":"794d963b8dd5187ee240d43134b47e249e04a73a","tid":1114853,"uid":78445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T18:21:03.000Z","msg":"我都面對同樣情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢又係以前番工唔知比咩人跣過一獲 我都唔知可以點做"},{"pid":"57209eb248923c434c82d0adb273e2b1c7522915","tid":1114853,"uid":16624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T18:23:35.000Z","msg":"用盡辦法同佢睇醫生，惡化得可以非常快就有尋死可能<br />\n衷心祝福"},{"pid":"ea80d764a08e91a76a6d2eea972fd638e5d7402f","tid":1114853,"uid":158227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T18:26:43.000Z","msg":"見臨床心理學家啦"},{"pid":"ef3aeebfacb305865dc3d1910e58b5b4a17424f2","tid":1114853,"uid":122570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T18:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"852ded66afe8a62e221c108596418663d8cf1e74","tid":1114853,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T11:11:04.000Z","msg":"報警"},{"pid":"2931dfff7a4584c5146442acf00ea54377897307","tid":1114853,"uid":38842,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T15:08:13.000Z","msg":"可以搵精神健康綜合社區中心幫幫手先<br />\n等啲社工同佢建立關係先.<br />\n跟住再一步步帶佢求醫<br />\n<br />\n各區地址:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.swd.gov.hk/tc/index/site_geoinfomap/page_rehabmap/sub_cssmap/id_iccmwmap/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Findex%2Fsite_geoinfomap%2Fpage_rehabmap%2Fsub_cssmap%2Fid_iccmwmap%2F&d=kjYWGV%2FOxf%2BJAuwkXUN1dJKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=90687239\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.swd.gov.hk/tc/index/site_geoinfomap/page_rehabmap/sub_cssmap/id_iccmwmap/</a>"},{"pid":"28b0ee77ff5893cb1ab8dbd2c0c821b21fd40f7b","tid":1114853,"uid":171786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T15:29:23.000Z","msg":"係唔係撞邪呀"},{"pid":"547e5b13e5872f7eca1858a8086b15452786a621","tid":1114853,"uid":40503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T15:52:19.000Z","msg":"Paranoid. <br />\n如果你肯定佢嘅疑神疑鬼係實無其事，<br />\n佢有需要睇醫生。"},{"pid":"3907a47613ba4acea2b3d3ef8adc4ac887602980","tid":1114853,"uid":144640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T15:55:55.000Z","msg":"可以試下打ha mental health direct個